{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>You're in Hell - Now what?</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ricardo the chicken was sent to Hell for bad boy crimes <i>(being cool)</i>, and now he must find a way back to his world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/AboutPage1.png?t=1739575403\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/AboutPage1.gif?t=1739575403\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Explore different landscapes</u></strong> in search of the Hell Bels, devices that open the exit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/AboutPage2.png?t=1739575403\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/AboutPage2.gif?t=1739575403\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Jump</strong></u> high, <strong><u>dash</u></strong> a lot, and <strong><u>grind</u></strong> icy rails!\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grab <strong><u>powerups</u></strong> to improve your abilities - They provide Ricardo with <i>gnarly accessories</i> too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/AboutPage3.png?t=1739575403\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/AboutPage3.gif?t=1739575403\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Of course there are enemies. And lots of fire. <u><strong>This IS Hell</strong></u>, after all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/AboutPage4.png?t=1739575403\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weird allies? Premonitions of disaster? No one seems to know for sure. <strong><i>They could be useful, though...</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you have what it takes to return home and take your life back?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Then stop the <strong><u>ultimate evil</u></strong> blocking your way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/PageBottom.png?t=1739575403\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3510020?t=1739575403","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739575403","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/065669e72e7e67efecf60b9ad788233e45ff5ac7/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739575403","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/065669e72e7e67efecf60b9ad788233e45ff5ac7/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739575403","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play on TV","id":43}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>You're in Hell - Now what?</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ricardo the chick